<p class="">What is wrong with it?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-b48e8ebc-a76f-4fdb-8ffe-b8c81ce26289" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
