<p class="">They have troops in Korea.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-52da4bb4-c891-4d66-84ec-e69a3e96fb3b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
