                Mr. Godfrey Nicholson  (Farnham)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-b8e75d76-8557-4ca4-aaee-5994c1b6e395" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1953-02-05/debates/279b2c6c-6d3c-419b-9cd3-f63ffbcdf7fd/FarEasternSituation#contribution-b8e75d76-8557-4ca4-aaee-5994c1b6e395">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
