<p class="">I did not say that while I was there the American people as a whole approved of this specific step in policy, if only for the good reason that it had not then occurred. I said that the mass of the American people were in favour of some fresh initiative to end the present impasse.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
